uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.util

Class KList<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.util.KList<V>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ISlotValues, KKeyedList, KSimpleList

    public abstract class KList<V>
extends java.lang.Object
    Base-class for classes that represent ordered lists whose update-operations can be listened to. Provides standard and some non-standard list-operations, plus methods for attaching listeners to listen for the results of those operations.
